Product Description

Red Furry Heart Shape Cushion

 

These decorative soft heart shaped scatter cushions are perfect for adding a loving touch to the bedroom or living room.

They are stuffed with a hollow fibre stuffing.

They measure approx 31cm wide x 38 cm high.

All fabric is from a smoke and pet free environment.
